videos.description: Needing a touchdown to match Texas Tech in the first overtime, Desmon White hauls in the ridiculous catch one handed against his helmet and controlling the ball all the way to the wall to tie the game for TCU at 24-24.
videos.headline: White's ridiculous TD catch in OT keeps TCU alive

videos.description: Brandon Hatfield 39 yd FG MISSED his 3rd miss of the game
videos.headline: TCU misses go ahead field goal in 2nd overtime

videos.description: After TCU missed a field goal to start the second overtime, Clayton Hatfield drills his kick from 37 yards away to give Texas Tech the thrilling 27-24 win.
videos.headline: Texas Tech completes upset with FG in 2OT
